24
00:03:07,560 --> 00:03:09,240
Kong, are you heartsick?

25
00:03:15,160 --> 00:03:16,240
Fine.

26
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,920
Apologies then.

27
00:03:19,160 --> 00:03:20,920
