28
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:21,880
Are you going?

29
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:22,400
I’m going.

30
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,480
I’m going too.

31
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:25,280
What the…

32
00:03:26,640 --> 00:03:28,360
I have to guard our stuff then.

33
00:03:35,520 --> 00:03:37,120
Hello, Nong Kong.

34
00:03:37,680 --> 00:03:39,640
Sawasdee krup, P’Ple.

35
00:03:40,440 --> 00:03:41,560
How are you?

36
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:45,120
I heard the fourth-year seniors intervened the freshman gathering today.

37
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,120
Yes.

38
00:03:46,160 --> 00:03:47,880
But… they didn’t tell us to do anything

39
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:50,000
