40
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:51,000
Oh, really?

41
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:55,080
But I think they are quite soft on you guys this year.

42
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:57,080
In the past we had to run like a hundred of lap, you know?

43
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:00,480
Why did they have to go to that extent

44
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:03,480
Everything they do,

45
00:04:03,480 --> 00:04:05,880
I’m sure they have reasons behind it

46
00:04:06,120 --> 00:04:07,320
What about you?

47
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:08,720
How are you holding up?

48
