I just tried to settle in bit by bit.

54
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:26,640
After a while, I found that it was not all bad.

55
00:04:26,640 --> 00:04:29,640
next think I know, I had already passed it all.

56
00:04:29,960 --> 00:04:32,440
And when I look back at it,

57
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,320
it was kind of fun actually.

58
00:04:40,400 --> 00:04:42,120
Is this what you are looking for?

59
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,440
Yeah. Thank you.

60
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:47,280
It was nice talking to you

61
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:48,680
but I think I should get back to my papers now.

62
00:04:48,960 --> 00:04:50,400
See you around, okay?

63
00:04:51,160 --> 00:04:52,360
Uh…P’Ple.

64
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,640
Actually, I wanted to study in economics.

65
00:04:58,240 --> 00:04:59,560
So right now,

66
00:04:59,560 --> 00:05:02,200
