69
00:05:10,600 --> 00:05:12,960
I think you better figure it out by yourself.

70
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:16,240
Even if I tell you, it’s just my own viewpoints.

71
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:18,600
You must find it out yourself

72
00:05:18,760 --> 00:05:21,200
