Hey, don’t forget that we have a physics test tomorrow.

78
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:21,840
Gosh, physics test!

79
00:06:23,280 --> 00:06:24,880
The lecture note I took…

80
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,160
