81
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:28,280
Has anyone had the lecture summary? Can I borrow?

82
00:06:28,880 --> 00:06:33,120
No one takes note these days. We use this.

83
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,560
Hey, you guys.

84
00:06:39,080 --> 00:06:40,200
Look over there.

85
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,360
Is that P’Arthit?

86
00:06:43,520 --> 00:06:44,840
