90
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,480
Yeah, what’s up?

91
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:21,080
Not yet. What’s the matter?

92
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,040
All right.

93
00:08:18,120 --> 00:08:20,080
P’Arthit, please stop.

94
00:08:21,640 --> 00:08:23,120
What are you doing here?

95
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:24,720
Leave me alone!

96
00:08:24,720 --> 00:08:26,720
